<mvc:View
	xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc"
	xmlns="sap.m"
	displayBlock="true"
	height="100%"
	xmlns:c="sap.ui.core"
	busyIndicatorDelay="0"
>
	<Page id="idPage">
		<customHeader>
			<Toolbar id="idToolbar">
				<Button
					id="idAddOrderButton"
					text="Add Order"
				/>
			</Toolbar>
		</customHeader>
		<Table
			id="idOrdersTable"
			items="{ODataModel>/Orders}"
		/>
		<Select
			id="idVendorsSelect"
			items="{/Vendors}"
		>
			<items>
				<c:Item id="idItem"/>
			</items>
		</Select>
		<Button id="idButton"/>
		<Button id="id0Button"/>
	</Page>
</mvc:View>
